#: changelog.py:5
msgid "When recording a voice or video message, NVDA now announces \"Recording a voice message\" or \"Recording a video message\" along with the elapsed time, instead of \"Tn voice message\"."
msgstr "錄製語音或視訊訊息時，NVDA 現在會朗讀「正在錄製語音訊息」或「正在錄製視訊訊息」並念出經過時間，而不再是「Tn voice message」。"


msgid "Microphone on"
msgstr "麥克風開啟"

msgid "Microphone muted"
msgstr "麥克風靜音"

msgid "Microphone button not found"
msgstr "找不到麥克風按鈕"

msgid "Camera button not found"
msgstr "找不到鏡頭按鈕"

msgid "This release restores compatibility with Unigram 12.7, where several shortcuts and announcements had stopped working."
msgstr "此版本修復了與 Unigram 12.7 的相容性，先前有多個快速鍵與語音提示失效。"

msgid "Poll messages again announce the question and answer options, and the forum topic list again announces the message preview."
msgstr "投票訊息會再次朗讀問題與答案選項，論壇主題清單會再次朗讀訊息預覽。"

msgid "During a one-to-one call, the mute microphone (ALT+A), enable or disable camera (ALT+V) and end call (ALT+N) shortcuts work again, and ALT+End again moves to the latest message."
msgstr "一對一通話中，靜音麥克風（ALT+A）、開啟或關閉鏡頭（ALT+V）與結束通話（ALT+N）的快速鍵可再次使用，ALT+End 會再次回到最新訊息。"

msgid "Rich message"
msgstr "豐富訊息"

msgid "Rich message. Press Alt+C to browse"
msgstr "豐富訊息。按 Alt+C 瀏覽"

msgid "Added support for rich messages. Rich messages are now announced when focused and can be opened with Alt+C in a browseable window."
msgstr "新增豐富訊息支援。豐富訊息取得焦點時會被朗讀，並可按 Alt+C 在可瀏覽視窗中開啟。"

msgid "Links and mixed content in rich messages are preserved, and links can be activated from the browseable window."
msgstr "豐富訊息中的連結與混合內容會被保留，且可在可瀏覽視窗中啟用連結。"

msgid "Fixed automatic updates: releases are now retrieved securely from GitHub and the downloaded add-on is validated before installation."
msgstr "修正自動更新：現在會從 GitHub 安全取得版本，並在安裝前驗證下載的附加元件。"
